title: Ebro In The Morning - The Aftermath of Overturning Roe V. Wade
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/27/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the monumental Supreme Court overturn of Roe V. Wade, the impact of stripping women of a fundamental right, and the BET Awards.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
